        """
        :type s: str
        :type t: str
        :rtype: str
        """
        
        if len(s) < len(t):
            return ""
        
        t_count = Counter(t)
        s_count = Counter()
        left = 0
        right = 0
        min_len = len(s) + 1
        min_left = 0
        min_right = 0

            s_count[s[right]] += 1
            if s_count[s[right]] <= t_count[s[right]]:
                right += 1
            while s_count[s[left]] > t_count[s[left]]:
                s_count[s[left]] -= 1
                left += 1
            if right - left < min_len:
                min_len = right - left
                min_left = left

            right += 1
